------------------------------------------------------------------------
TWEAK SLIDECASTING
------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. INSTALLATION

You have to create an bookmark with following url content:

javascript:(function(){if(document.getElementById('tweakdashboard')===null){var%20script=document.createElement('script');script.src='http://localhost/stefan/uni/interface/tweakslidecasting/tweak.js';document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(script);}})()

This code will load and start the javascript file from the git repository.
As a result a red box with commands should appear at the top left corner.

To properly reload the script, you have to reload the page and click the bookmark again.


2. TWEAKS

 * general:
   - maximize/minimize main content
   - history function for sub pages (with some exceptions, eg. 'portfolio' functions)

 * slides:
   - overall show/hide of notes
   - show/hide per note
   - sub menus:
     - on click, close other sub menus
   - date menu:
     - direct access to 'all' slides and further horizontal/vertical view


3. BROWSER SUPPORT

Testing with:

 * Mozilla Firefox 3.6.11
 * Google Chrome 5.0.375.126
